title: InitializeBACnetDateRange (Function)
text:
FUNCTION InitializeBACnetDateRange : BOOL
Initializes a IEC_BACNET_DATE_RANGE according to a given BACnetDateRange struct.

rows.Name: dateRange
rows.Comment: The BACnetDateRange to use for initialization.

rows.Name: bacDateRange
rows.Comment: The BACnet date range to operate on.
